txt.en: 'Stupids! Stupids! Siege engine not go through mud!'
'If war machine not go to North Downs, I get flogged! But you get killed! I kill you myself!'
'Where did other wheel pushers go? Lazy stupid Orcs!'
'Stop. We rest now. Not kill off last few Orcs.'
'Yes! Me good leader! Still got three Orcs left to push war-wagon!'
'Only two of you left? What? Started with ten! Stupid Orcs die on the way!'
'Not talk back, stupids! Catapult smaller than war-wagon, but got small wheels, too, get stuck in mud easy.'
'Lazy stupid Orcs! Move machine or die!'
'Yes, I know. Too kind to slave Orcs. See?  You can rest now.'
'I say you can rest, not you can sleep! Wake up, lazy Orcs!'
'Hope Iron Crown man know, not got enough Orcs to move cart fast. Not my fault we so late!'
